title: Prince Albert and Princess Charlene of Monaco enjoy low-key Irish holiday
text: Prince Albert and Princess Charlene of Monaco enjoy low-key Irish holiday Independent.ie Prince Albert and Princess Charlene of Monaco have returned to Ireland with an informal visit to County Louth. http://www.independent.ie/style/celebrity/celebrity-news/prince-albert-and-princess-charlene-of-monaco-enjoy-lowkey-irish-holiday-35349188.html http://www.independent.ie/incoming/article35349186.ece/844a1/AUTOCROP/h342/monasterboice.JPG Princess Charlene enters The Monasterboice Inn ahead of Prince Albert (in baseball cap) yesterday afternoon. Photo: Fran Caffrey/ Newsfile. Prince Albert II of Monaco and Princess Charlene arrive to attend the 68th annual Red Cross Gala Prince Albert and Princess Charlene of Monaco have returned to Ireland with an informal visit to County Louth.
